Navigating the vast metropolis of London can be a daunting task for even the most experienced travelers, but with this guide, you will have everything you need to explore the city with ease!

In this indispensable guide to a real British experience, you will find:

A complete list of London's top attractions and hidden gems, so you can experience the city like a local;
Experts' strategic advices on the best places to stay, best restaurants and bars to enjoy London safely;
9 tips on how to avoid overwhelming crowds, skip the lines and discover hidden sights and sounds;
Lots of smart itineraries to effectively organize your days, with stunning photographs and maps of London
Tips on how to get in touch with the local culture, from enjoying a pint in a traditional pub to attending local and cultural events
The 5 suggestions you absolutely must know about currency exchange and foreign ATMs to avoid excessive fees and criminal activities;
BONUS: A checklist of everything you need to pack before your trip!
